  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-7-104.3, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE STARKVILLE-OKTIBBEHA CONSOLIDATED SCHOOL DISTRICT AND MISSISSIPPI STATE UNIVERSITY TO ENTER INTO CERTAIN AGREEMENTS CONCERNING JOINTLY UTILIZED PRIMARY AND SECONDARY EDUCATION FACILITIES; TO FURTHER AUTHORIZE THE SCHOOL DISTRICT AND UNIVERSITY TO TRANSFER AND EXPEND SUCH FUNDS ON MUTUALLY AGREEABLE TERMS AND CONDITIONS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
